imdb.plot outline: Script Magazine is proud to announce "Development Hell and Back." Hosted by Hammad Zaidi and John W. Kim, will cover a comprehensive look at screenwriters and their craft, from interviews with A-list scribes to discussions with industry producers and current development executives, agents, and managers.
